high_descs: Turn around and face the counter in front of you.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the lettuce on the counter on your left.
Slice the lettuce in front of you.
Turn left and open the cabinet under the counter in front of you.
Place the knife inside of the cabinet and close it.
Face the lettuce on the counter to your right.
Take a lettuce slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge to your left.
Place the lettuce inside the fridge in front of you for a bit then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn left and face the sink in front of you.
Place the lettuce in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold lettuce slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right then face the counter on your right then look at the bread knife
Pick up the bread knife on the counter
Turn right then face the cabbage on your left
Slice the cabbage
Make a step and face the cabinet on your left
Open the first cabinet and put in the bread knife
Turn right face the cabbage
Pick up the slice of cabbage
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the cabbage then close the fridge
Turn left then head to the sink on your right
Put the cabbage in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled sliced cabbage in the sink

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right, move to the cabinet right of the stove.
Put the knife in the lower cabinet.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the counter, in front of the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of chilled lettuce in the sink.
